719569f-a.title: Manhattan: East River Drive - 81st Street (East)
719569f-a.text:
East River Drive, north from East 81st Street, showing
a portion of the new circumfrential highway and the
surrounding locale at this point. The apartment houses
above constitute Gracie Scuare.
September 29, 1940
No's. 1-2-3
P. L. Sperr

719570f-b.title: Manhattan: East River Drive - 81st Street (East)
719570f-b.text:
East River Drive, at the foot of East 81st Street, show
ing details of the over-pass above the new viaduct. in
the background are the Triboro and Hellgate Bridges.
September 29, 1940
No's. 1-2
P. L. Sperr
